# Epic Routes — Firebase (Archive)

Minimal archive repo containing legal pages for a Firebase-hosted Epic Routes workflow.

## Contents

- `privacy-policy.html` — privacy policy page
- `terms-of-service.html` — terms of service page

## Purpose

Static HTML legal documents. Not an active application codebase. Preserve existing HTML structure and legal wording unless explicitly asked to update copy.

## Coding preferences

- Edit HTML only when requested; keep styles inline or as-is
- Do not add build tooling, frameworks, or dependencies to this archive
- Match existing formatting and section structure when making edits
